:<!--Trigger PerformanceE 802610239: Config/Level/Mission/8026102/Act/Act802610239.json-->
;(If {{cx}}<!--SubMission Started: 802612102-->)
::'''Montana:''' Festive Superstar! That was awesome!
::'''Montana:''' First, when I was checking on the stage equipment, I noticed there was an unfinished track inside. After that, I asked the band and others to help finish this song with all the Inspiration you gathered!
::'''Montana:''' We can start a performance at any time. Wanna try?
::<!--Custom String Trigger: FinishMission8026121-->
;(If {{cx}}<!--SubMission not Started: 802612102-->)
::'''Montana:''' Festive Superstar! The music party hasn't ended yet. Is there something you need since you specifically came by the stage?
:<!--Custom String Trigger: Wait_Option_802610239_88-->
:<!--Custom String Listener: Wait_Option_802610239_88-->
:{{DIcon|Travel Log}} Prepare for the band performance.
::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_802610903-->
::'''Montana:''' Got it. Even with Lady Rappa's departure, the Dazzling's music will never stop playing!
::<!--Custom String Trigger: OpenUI_MusicRhythm-->
::<!--Ends the current performance-->
:{{DIcon|Talk}} Can we have a chat?
::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_802610905-->
::'''Montana:''' Sure. Decorating the stage is kinda boring, but then again, as the Festive Superstar, is there anything you would like to know?
::<!--Custom String Trigger: Wait_Option_802610239_93-->
::<!--Custom String Listener: Wait_Option_802610239_93-->
::{{DIcon|Talk}} About the new tune...
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_802610907-->
:::'''Montana:''' Oh right! When I was checking on the stage equipment, I noticed there was an unfinished track inside.
:::'''Montana:''' Maybe Lady Rappa left it behind? I'm not too sure either... but if you can collect enough composition inspiration, the remaining band members might be able to finish the track.
:::'''Montana:''' Give it a try! The stage show is going to continue, so it'd be a bigger blast with new music!
::;(Return to previous option selection (cloneCheckString))
::{{DIcon|Talk}} The band's reviews...
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_802610911-->
:::'''Montana:''' That closing show at the end was deffo the most exciting performance I've ever witnessed, bar none!
:::'''Montana:''' Lady Rappa's surprise reveal, everyone else's freestyling, and the showdown between the Festive Superstar and the academy's representative... It's spread across the school like wildfire, and everyone on campus can't stop talking about it!
:::'''Montana:''' *sigh* After witnessing such a powerful performance, the other celebration activities appear bland in comparison.
::;(Return to previous option selection (cloneCheckString))
::{{DIcon|Talk}} About the music party...
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_802610915-->
:::'''Montana:''' The music party is the grandest event of the Dreamlight Anniversary celebration. It's also a time that all students look forward to!
:::'''Montana:''' Everyone is busy preparing for the celebration, and the campus is filled with fun booths and activities. Just wandering around is enough to make you feel overwhelmed. Freedom and joy &mdash; this is what the atmosphere of a college should feel like.
:::'''Montana:''' Needless to say... there's also such an exciting performance!
:::<!--Custom String Trigger: Wait_Option_802610239_106-->
:::<!--Custom String Listener: Wait_Option_802610239_106-->
:::{{DIcon|Talk}} How long will the music party last?
::::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_802610919-->
::::'''Montana:''' According to past experience, the music party and the Dreamlight Anniversary celebration will end at the same time. But there are people who are constantly asking for the event time to be extended. No one really knows for sure how long this will last.
::::'''Montana:''' As for us, of course, we'd like it to last as long as possible.
:::;(Return to previous option selection (cloneCheckString))
:::{{DIcon|Talk}} The music party is related to the three academies?
::::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_802610922-->
::::'''Montana:''' Although the music party is a student initiative, it's still influenced by the various schools.
::::'''Montana:''' For example... back then, the band leader was often appointed by Charmony Academy, while Fortune Academy would set requirements for the scale and duration of the performance. As for Dreamweaver Academy, it was straightforward &mdash; members just needed to have a sufficient grade.
::::'''Montana:''' But this time, having students from outside the academies... having Rappa and the Festive Superstar directing the band is the first of its kind, so it's kinda special!
:::;(Return to previous option selection (cloneCheckString))
:::{{DIcon|Talk}} Is the music party very important?
::::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_802610926-->
::::'''Montana:''' What did the academy's representative say... "The music party is a showcase of the energy and creativity of Paperfold University." But the students don't care about this. They only want the event to be interesting.
::::'''Montana:''' So please don't be pressured, Festive Superstar! Just go with your gut and play your hearts out!
:::;(Return to previous option selection (cloneCheckString))
:::{{DIcon|Return}} I've just about got everything.
::::<!--Custom String Listener: Wait_Option_802610239_93-->
::::{{DIcon|Talk}} About the new tune...
:::::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_802610907-->
:::::'''Montana:''' Oh right! When I was checking on the stage equipment, I noticed there was an unfinished track inside.
:::::'''Montana:''' Maybe Lady Rappa left it behind? I'm not too sure either... but if you can collect enough composition inspiration, the remaining band members might be able to finish the track.
:::::'''Montana:''' Give it a try! The stage show is going to continue, so it'd be a bigger blast with new music!
::::;(Return to previous option selection (cloneCheckString))
::::{{DIcon|Talk}} The band's reviews...
:::::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_802610911-->
:::::'''Montana:''' That closing show at the end was deffo the most exciting performance I've ever witnessed, bar none!
:::::'''Montana:''' Lady Rappa's surprise reveal, everyone else's freestyling, and the showdown between the Festive Superstar and the academy's representative... It's spread across the school like wildfire, and everyone on campus can't stop talking about it!
:::::'''Montana:''' *sigh* After witnessing such a powerful performance, the other celebration activities appear bland in comparison.
::::;(Return to previous option selection (cloneCheckString))
:::;(<!--Return to previous option selection (cloneCheckString)-->)
::::{{DIcon|Talk}} About the central stage...
:::::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_802610930-->
:::::'''Montana:''' Can you see that huge glittering golden bird above us? Isn't it super stylish?
:::::'''Montana:''' This design is specifically created for this music party by Dreamweaver Academy. It's both trendy and cool, befitting the theme of the performance. Once it's set up, it'll become the highlight of the entire school.
:::::'''Montana:''' I hear that it'll be on the cover page of the next issue of ''Dreamchaser Bulletin''. Many students want to climb up and take a selfie with the bird!
::::;(Return to previous option selection (cloneCheckString))
::::{{DIcon|Exit}} That's all.
:::::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_802610934-->
:::::'''Montana:''' Okay! Go be busy, Festive Superstar! Leave the stage work to me!
:::::<!--Custom String Trigger: ALL_TALK_END-->
:::::<!--Custom String Listener: ALL_TALK_END-->
:::::<!--Ends the current performance-->
