:{{DIcon|?}} Do you need me for something?
::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_802610936-->
::'''Montana:''' Ah, just in time! Umm... The school's come out with a yearbook, and it's got a page that's kinda like a message wall for everyone to leave notes. I'd like to ask you to write something in it for me, Festive Superstar!
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} Why didn't I receive this news?
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_802610938-->
:::'''Montana:''' Maybe because the yearbook's still in the content collection phase. You're the Festive Superstar, so you'll probably only get the final version after the school's curated it. It's still early days.
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} Sure, what kind of tone do you want it in?
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_802610940-->
:::'''Montana:''' Anything's good! Anything written by you is an honor for me!
::<!--Custom String Trigger: TalkSentence_802610941-->
::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_802610941-->
::'''Montana:''' Please help me out. The other band members have also filled it up. It's just you left...
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} (Write a serious message)
